#

Pickle and Hummus Dip

10 min
$8
150 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

DairyGarlic

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

SnackDipEasy

Description

A zesty and creamy dip that's perfect for snacking or entertaining, combining the tanginess of pickles with the smoothness of hummus.

Ingredients

  • hummus: 1 cup
  • dill pickles: 1/2 cup, chopped
  • cream cheese: 1/2 cup, softened
  • garlic powder: 1/2 teaspoon
  • lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
  • fresh dill: 1 tablespoon, chopped (optional)
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
